<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA516_12_IH_0001</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema516_12.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema516_12_ih_0001 paging">
      <section class="title type2 score">
        <h2 data-head="1" lang="y">마름모의 넓이를 두 가지 방법으로 구하려고 합니다. 물음에 답해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>
      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3>
            <span lang="y">마름모를 둘러싸는 직사각형을 그렸습니다.</span>
            <span class="nemo"></span>
            <span lang="y">안에 알맞은 수를 써넣으세요.</span>
          </h3>
          <div class="question_box dir_col justify_center">
            <div class="img_area">
              <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA516_12_IH/0001_01.png" alt="" />
              <p class="text_square_bg">1 ㎠</p>
              <p class="text_square_bg">1 ㎠</p>
            </div>
            <div class="input_area mt_20">
              <span lang="y">(마름모의 넓이) =(그린 직사각형의 넓이)÷2=</span>
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span>×</span>
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="6"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span>÷2=</span>
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="12"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span>(㎠)</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 해설 -->
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y">(마름모의 넓이) =(그린 직사각형의 넓이)÷2 =(가로) (세로)÷2=4×6÷2=12 (㎠)</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3>
            <span lang="y">마름모를 둘러싸는 직사각형을 그렸습니다.</span>
            <span class="nemo"></span>
            <span lang="y">안에 알맞은 수를 써넣으세요.</span>
          </h3>
          <div class="question_box dir_col justify_center">
            <div class="img_area">
              <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA516_12_IH/0001_02.png" alt="" />
              <p class="text_square_bg">1 ㎠</p>
              <p class="text_square_bg">1 ㎠</p>
              <p class="text1" lang="y">높이</p>
              <p class="text2" lang="y">밑변</p>
            </div>
            <div class="input_area mt_20">
              <span lang="y">(마름모의 넓이)=(만든 평행사변형의 넓이)=</span>
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span>×</span>
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="6"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span>÷2=</span>
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="12"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span>(㎠)</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 해설 -->
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y">(마름모의 넓이)=(만든 평행사변형의 넓이) =(밑변의 길이)×(높이) =4×(6÷2) =4×3=12 (㎠)</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
